				</li>
			</ol>
			<!-- antwoorden uitklap -->
			<div class="hider">
				<div class="showhide">&rarr;</div>
				<div class="antwoord"><p>Antwoord bij F- en Z-hoeken
					<ol>
						<li>De hoeken &ang;<em>C</em><sub>12</sub> en &ang;<em>E</em><sub>1</sub> vormen een F-hoek.<br>
						De hoeken &ang;<em>B</em> en &ang;<em>D</em><sub>3</sub> ook.</li>
						<li>De hoeken &ang;<em>C</em><sub>2</sub> en &ang;<em>D</em><sub>2</sub> vormen een Z-hoek</li>
						<li><u>Hoekensom</u>: &ang;<em>D</em><sub>1</sub> zit in &Delta;<em>BCD</em>. Dus <nobr>68&deg; + 30&deg; + &ang;<em>D</em><sub>1</sub></nobr> moet 180&deg; zijn.<br>
							Dus &ang;<em>D</em><sub>1</sub> = 180 - 68 - 30 = 82&deg;.</li>
						<li><u>Hoekensom</u>: &ang;<em>C</em><sub>12</sub> zit in &Delta;<em>ABC</em>. Dus <nobr>54 + 68 + &ang;<em>C</em><sub>12</sub></nobr> moet 180&deg; zijn.<br>
							Dus &ang;<em>C</em><sub>12</sub> = 180 - 54 - 68 = 58&deg;.<br>
							&ang;<em>C</em><sub>12</sub> = &ang;<em>C</em><sub>1</sub> + &ang;<em>C</em><sub>2</sub>, dus &ang;<em>C</em><sub>1</sub> = 28&deg;</li>
						<li>
							<ul>
								<li><u>Z-hoek</u>: &ang;<em>C</em><sub>1</sub> = &ang;<em>D</em><sub>2</sub> = 30&deg;</li>
								<li><u>F-hoek</u>: &ang;<em>B</em> = &ang;<em>D</em><sub>3</sub> = 68&deg;<br>
									<u>Gestrekte hoek</u>: &ang;<em>D</em><sub>123</sub> = 180&deg;, dus &ang;<em>D</em><sub>3</sub> = 180 - 82 - 30 = 68</li>
								<li><u>F-hoek</u>: &ang;<em>C</em><sub>12</sub> = &ang;<em>E</em><sub>1</sub> = 58&deg;<br>
									of: <u>Hoekensom</u>: Er moet gelden dat &ang;<em>A</em> + &ang;<em>D</em><sub>3</sub> + &ang;<em>E</em><sub>1</sub> = 180&deg;<br>
									Dus &ang;<em>E</em><sub>1</sub> = 180 - 54 - 68 = 58&deg;</li>
								<li><u>Gestrekte hoek</u>: &ang;<em>E</em><sub>12</sub> = 180&deg;, dus &ang;<em>E</em><sub>2</sub> = 180 - 58 = 122&deg;</li>
							</ul>
						</li>
					</ol>
				</p></div>
			</div>
		</p>
	</div>

